folder: Exchange Place & New Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
(1)
Exchange Place, north side, from New, to Broad Streets. In the foreground, appears the excavation on the site of the former Johnstone Building, at No. 30 Broad Street.

September 16, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, from a different angle. Building standing between excavations, is the Ocean Cable Offices, at No. 38-40 Broad Street.

September 16, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
